### Issue description

This test passed with RunTest but failed with DebugTest
```
    [TestClass]
    public class UnitTest1 {
        [TestMethod]
        public void TestMethod1() {
            using(var form = new System.Windows.Forms.Form()) {
                bool formWasPaint = false;
                form.Paint += (s, e) => {
                    formWasPaint = true;
                };
                form.Show();
                Application.DoEvents();
                Assert.IsTrue(formWasPaint);
            }
        }
    }
```
With MSTest 3.0.4

### Steps to reproduce

1. Create new MSTest project
2. Add Windows Forms support (TargetFramework and UseWindowsForms in  csproj file)
3. Add test with source code above
4. Try RunTest and try DebugTest ... you will see different result and you will not see the form DebugTest case
